data.description: Darling well cared home on 1.6 acres in Klamath County. Taxes are only $950.32 a year. Circular drive Lots of room for a shop, but home has a very nice carport. New deck on back of home. fenced on 3 sides. Backs a large parcel. Home has wood stove, and the furnace runs on propane.
